Import your Google Ads campaigns

Save time by importing your Google Ads campaigns into Bing Ads to get ads live quickly.


Sign in with your Microsoft account (or create one) to get started on Bing Ads.


From within the Bing Ads interface, select the Import from Google Ads option.


Enter your Google Ads credentials and select the campaign you want to import.









